# Stack & Components

## Framework & Styling
- **Next.js 15** for the app (App Router, React Server Components where appropriate).
- **Tailwind CSS** for all styling. Prefer utility classes; avoid inline styles or separate CSS files for component styles.
- **Shadcn/ui** for UI components. Use Shadcn primitives instead of building from scratch.

## Buttons & Primitives
- **Never use raw `<button>`**. Use Radix-based primitives (e.g. Shadcn `Button`, which uses Radix under the hood).
- Prefer Shadcn components: `Button`, `Dialog`, `DropdownMenu`, `Select`, `Tabs`, etc.

## Animations
- Use **Framer Motion** (`motion`, `AnimatePresence`) for animations and transitions.
- Avoid CSS-only animation libraries when Framer Motion can handle the interaction.

## Layout & Spacing
- Keep layouts **spacious**. Use `gap-8` or larger (e.g. `gap-8`, `gap-10`, `gap-12`) for flex/grid containers.
- Prefer semantic layout primitives (flex, grid) with consistent gap scale.
